name: MAZE 2D (MoonTaehyung)
description:
Rules:

You need to eat the "small" green monsters first, and then ,"big" black monsters . Otherwise, the black monsters will eat you!!! 

You have to eat all the monsters in the game in order to proceed to next level! 

Green monsters - 10 points each.

Black monsters- 20 points each.

You have endless lives to play in this maze! There  are total 3 levels in this game. Hope you enjoy the game!

Please leave a feedback :) Thank you.

PS: The assets(monsters) used in the game were not developed by me. I have taken them from the website-opengameart.org.Credits go to the original creators.
